{"title":"This Drust Cargo Touring Bike is For Sale","link":"https://theradavist.com/drust-cargo-bike-for-sale","date":1777366889000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-For-Sale.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-For-Sale.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-For-Sale.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-For-Sale.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Yesterday, our <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2026-bespoked-uk-drust-cycles-cargo-bikes\" target=\"_blank\">Drust Cycles Pinion gallery</a> sent ripples through space and time. From stoked kiddos to silly colors, it had everything a cargophile would want. John got a flood of DMs on Instagram, asking what it was like ordering a custom bike from Drust. Many people said they wouldn’t know what or how to order.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-for-Sale-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-for-Sale-2.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-for-Sale-2.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-for-Sale-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-for-Sale-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-for-Sale-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-for-Sale-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/04/Drust-for-Sale-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>This decisionphobia is real. Which is why it’s sometimes easier to buy a bike already made. Well, here’s your chance! This size XL Drust Cycles, as documented in <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/eurobike-2024-gallery-part-01#:~:text=tires%20were%20fine.-,In%20Drust%20We%20Trust,-Having%20spent%20a\" target=\"_blank\">our Eurobike 2024 coverage</a>, is for sale as a frameset with racks. If you’re interested and would like to know more, like sizing, shipping options, and pricing, send <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/drustcycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Konstantin a DM</a> or <a href=\"https://drustcycles.com/pages/contact\" target=\"_blank\">email</a>. Tell him we sent ya!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/drust-cargo-bike-for-sale\">This Drust Cargo Touring Bike is For Sale</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://cms.theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"a17f9f33df61164e3546443a972583acbccff1d136cb10f34aa4b53794b425f8","category":"Cycling"}